sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant View as View Layer<br/>(home.blade.php)
    participant Controller as Controller Layer<br/>(Livewire Component)
    participant Auth as Auth Facade
    participant UserModel as User Model
    participant DB as Database

    User->>View: Access /portal/home
    View->>Controller: Component initialization
    Controller->>Controller: Component mount (default)
    
    Controller-->>View: Render home page
    
    View->>Auth: auth()->user()
    Auth->>DB: Retrieve authenticated user session
    DB-->>Auth: User session data
    Auth-->>View: Current user instance
    
    View->>UserModel: $user->given_name
    UserModel-->>View: User's given name
    
    View->>View: now()->format('d F Y (l)')
    View-->>View: Current date formatted
    
    View->>View: Build static content:<br/>- Welcome card<br/>- Quick access cards<br/>- Carousel slides<br/>- Service sections
    
    View-->>User: Display portal home with:<br/>- Welcome message<br/>- Date display<br/>- Message notification<br/>- Quick access cards<br/>- Image carousel<br/>- Service links

    User->>View: Click "Calendar" card
    View->>Controller: wire:navigate to route('portal.calendar')
    Controller-->>View: Navigate to calendar page
    View-->>User: Redirect to calendar

    User->>View: Click "Student Activities" card
    View->>Controller: wire:navigate to route('portal.activities.list')
    Controller-->>View: Navigate to activities list
    View-->>User: Redirect to activities

    User->>View: Click "News & Announcement" card
    View->>Controller: wire:navigate to route('portal.news.list')
    Controller-->>View: Navigate to news list
    View-->>User: Redirect to news

    User->>View: Carousel auto-advance (8s interval)
    View->>View: Update active slide index
    View-->>User: Display next carousel slide

    User->>View: Click carousel slide
    View-->>User: Navigate to slide URL

    User->>View: Click "Profile" link
    View->>Controller: wire:navigate to route('portal.profile.personal-particular')
    Controller-->>View: Navigate to profile page
    View-->>User: Redirect to personal particulars

    User->>View: Click "News and Announcement" link
    View->>Controller: Navigate to route('portal.news.list')
    Controller-->>View: Navigate to news list
    View-->>User: Redirect to news

    User->>View: Click "Calendar" link (Student Affairs)
    View->>Controller: Navigate to route('portal.calendar')
    Controller-->>View: Navigate to calendar
    View-->>User: Redirect to calendar

    User->>View: Click "Student Activity" link
    View->>Controller: Navigate to route('portal.activities.list')
    Controller-->>View: Navigate to activities
    View-->>User: Redirect to activities

    User->>View: Click "Resources Centre" link
    View->>Controller: wire:navigate to route('portal.resources-centre')
    Controller-->>View: Navigate to resources
    View-->>User: Redirect to resources centre

    User->>View: Click "VTC Valo" external link
    View-->>User: Open external URL
